# generate_ansible.py

## Purpose
Scaffolds an Ansible playbook to deploy your application:
- Installs dependencies
- Deploys code
- Configures and starts services
- Ensures idempotency

## Prerequisites
- Python 3.8+
- `pip install ollama`
- SSH access or dynamic inventory for target hosts

## Usage
```sh
chmod +x generate_ansible.py
./generate_ansible.py \
  --model llama3.1:8b \
  --env staging \
  --output ansible/staging.yml

